snippet.textDisplay:
Mashallah, Allah ne aapko bahot pyari avaaz navazi hai.
Naatshareef ko gaa kr iss nemat ki aur Naatshareef ki beizzati naa karen.
Allah aapko Hidayat de, Atif Bhai. Paisa banane me koi gurayz nai, lekin Naat Shareef ko Ganey ki tarah gaa kr Naatshareef ko padhe janey ki izzatt uchaalre ho.
Allah aap ko Naatshareef padhne ki taufeek se navazey aur usey gana ki shakal me ganey se parhez karaye. Ameen!
